descriptionHtml:
11.0 updated arm movement per requests.
Here\'s a demo video link
http://youtu.be/O6NC3bx2Pes

10.0 updated all animations as requested to make things like legs not kick out and to change the fall animations.  Let me know what you think.  Just unzip and copy the meshes folder to your skyrim/data folder.  Mine is located at 
C:\\Program Files (x86)\\Steam\\steamapps\\common\\skyrim\\data

9.0 added left, right, backward animations


I added run, jump and fall animations to the list of animations. 

I used this mod to double her sprint speed.  Superfun!!!
Skyrim Speeds Application
http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=1603 

I created this to have something less butch to stare at when running out of a mine.
